<c.bg_transparent>I told him I had to help</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>someone with her homework.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:20:58.423 --> 00:20:59.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good thinking.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:21:00.175 --> 00:21:02.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Too bad I'll never</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>be able to use that lie.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:21:02.636 --> 00:21:05.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-My dad knows I never do homework.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's not a lie, Nog.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:21:05.264 --> 00:21:08.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mardah's studying entomology.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>She asked me to help her out.</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:21:08.976 --> 00:21:12.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A dabo girl who studies entomology?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Ha! Sure.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:21:12.521 --> 00:21:13.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's true.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:21:13.563 --> 00:21:14.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:21:18.277 --> 00:21:19.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is entomology?</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:21:20.237 --> 00:21:21.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The study of bugs.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:21:21.780 --> 00:21:23.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you mean she wants to be a chef?</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:21:27.119 --> 00:21:27.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, who's that?</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:21:28.495 --> 00:21:29.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>NOG: I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:21:32.124 --> 00:21:36.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's he doing? Oh, that's disgusting!</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:21:36.378 --> 00:21:39.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He must be one of those Skrreeans.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>My dad says there's a lot more on the way.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:21:43.302 --> 00:21:44.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hi!</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:21:46.596 --> 00:21:48.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doesn't he know what a replicator's for?</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:21:49.099 --> 00:21:49.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Idiot!</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:21:51.059 --> 00:21:54.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, does Mardah</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have any sisters?</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:22:00.610 --> 00:22:02.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'BRIEN: Commander</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've cleared the Skrreean ship</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:22:02.821 --> 00:22:03.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to dock at Upper Pylon 2.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:22:05.032 --> 00:22:08.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's time to welcome your people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Alpha Quadrant, Haneek.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:22:21.631 --> 00:22:24.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HANEEK: Come along, don't be afraid.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:22:24.634 --> 00:22:27.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come on, it's all right.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You're among friends.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:22:28.638 --> 00:22:31.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't be afraid.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:22:31.641 --> 00:22:32.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:22:34.436 --> 00:22:36.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( astonished murmuring )</c.bg_transparent>

340
