<c.bg_transparent>Slow down!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>There's no running on the Promenade.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:23:19.689 --> 00:23:22.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to get awfully crowded</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around here, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:23:22.609 --> 00:23:25.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, Constable, but it's worth it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Just look at them.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:23:26.530 --> 00:23:29.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're experiencing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their first taste of freedom.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:23:39.459 --> 00:23:41.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-JAKE: Nog, where you going?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Can't talk now. Gotta run!</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:23:41.545 --> 00:23:42.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nog!</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:23:43.338 --> 00:23:45.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know there's no running</c.bg_transparent>
