347
00:23:45.841 --> 00:23:46.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who's running?</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:23:47.759 --> 00:23:51.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What seems to be the problem here?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What's that smell?</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:23:51.263 --> 00:23:53.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Ask him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Me?</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:23:53.431 --> 00:23:54.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're the one who stinks.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:23:54.683 --> 00:23:56.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's because you sprayed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that vapor on us.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:23:56.935 --> 00:23:58.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that true, Nog?</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:23:58.687 --> 00:23:59.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No!</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:24:00.772 --> 00:24:01.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nog...</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:24:03.400 --> 00:24:04.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was a joke.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:24:05.861 --> 00:24:07.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very amusing.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:24:08.363 --> 00:24:09.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you for bringing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this to my attention.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:24:09.823 --> 00:24:11.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll take care of it from here.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:24:11.867 --> 00:24:12.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( squealing )</c.bg_transparent>

360
