<c.bg_transparent>for illegal weapon sales."</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:24:45.817 --> 00:24:48.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Weapon sales, huh? Very profitable.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:24:49.070 --> 00:24:52.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How would you know about that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-My Uncle Quark told me.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:24:53.783 --> 00:24:58.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And what would your Uncle Quark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>know about illegal weapon sales?</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:24:58.955 --> 00:25:01.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He, uh... he, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:25:01.458 --> 00:25:05.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Knows better than to ever</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>get involved in anything so disreputable.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:25:05.837 --> 00:25:06.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: I'm sure.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:25:07.589 --> 00:25:10.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I asked that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the boy's father come to see me.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:25:10.842 --> 00:25:14.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rom is doing the weekly stock inventory.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to interrupt him.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:25:14.721 --> 00:25:18.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know how easy he loses count.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>So, I came in his place.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:25:19.517 --> 00:25:22.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nog, have you been causing mischief again?</c.bg_transparent>

377
