379
00:25:29.027 --> 00:25:30.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Did he?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( laughing nervously )</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:25:31.196 --> 00:25:32.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you have to say for yourself?</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:25:33.990 --> 00:25:35.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I--I'm sorry?</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:25:35.492 --> 00:25:37.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see the boy's beside</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>himself with guilt.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:25:37.786 --> 00:25:42.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That doesn't excuse his actions.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And he will be punished severely.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:25:42.540 --> 00:25:43.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will?</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:25:44.167 --> 00:25:48.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to tell the Constable here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you will never do it again.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:25:49.798 --> 00:25:50.632 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't?</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:25:51.967 --> 00:25:55.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, I won't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I promise. Never again.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:25:55.720 --> 00:25:57.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>See that you don't.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:25:58.598 --> 00:26:00.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can I leave now?</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:26:02.894 --> 00:26:04.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:26:08.483 --> 00:26:10.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, you really can't blame the boy.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:26:11.194 --> 00:26:13.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-And why is that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, come on, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:26:14.155 --> 00:26:16.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know these Skrreeans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are nothing but trouble.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:26:16.658 --> 00:26:18.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're all over the station</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:26:18.451 --> 00:26:22.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>looking and touching,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>never buying anything.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:26:22.455 --> 00:26:25.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-And they flake.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I didn't notice.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:26:25.333 --> 00:26:29.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come to my place.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You'll see little pieces of Skrreean skin</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:26:29.212 --> 00:26:32.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>all over the bar and the floor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's disgusting.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:26:32.716 --> 00:26:34.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Well, they won't be here long.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I hope not.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:26:35.051 --> 00:26:36.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're driving my paying customers away.</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:26:37.137 --> 00:26:39.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They stay here too long,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I'll be out of business.</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:26:39.514 --> 00:26:42.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In that case,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I hope they never leave.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:26:48.023 --> 00:26:49.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( scoffs )</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:26:49.524 --> 00:26:51.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( excited chatter )</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:26:51.276 --> 00:26:53.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( wind instrument playing softly )</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:27:02.203 --> 00:27:08.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've talked it over among ourselves.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Our feelings were unanimous.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:27:09.169 --> 00:27:12.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You discovered the Eye of the Universe.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:27:13.131 --> 00:27:18.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must lead us the rest of the way.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:27:24.267 --> 00:27:26.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll do the best I can.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:27:39.115 --> 00:27:40.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That looked serious.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:27:42.327 --> 00:27:44.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is everything all right?</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:27:46.039 --> 00:27:47.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look at them.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:27:48.625 --> 00:27:50.085 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look at my people.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:27:52.045 --> 00:27:54.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never seen them so happy</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:27:55.715 --> 00:27:58.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and here I sit, feeling trapped.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:27:59.719 --> 00:28:00.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:28:00.970 --> 00:28:04.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They expect me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to lead them to Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:28:04.766 --> 00:28:06.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( music ends, crowd applauds)</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:28:06.976 --> 00:28:08.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to be okay.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:28:09.187 --> 00:28:13.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Sisko is doing everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he can to find you a place to live.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:28:14.109 --> 00:28:15.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not alone.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:28:15.443 --> 00:28:17.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope I'm not intruding.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:28:17.278 --> 00:28:18.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:28:18.988 --> 00:28:23.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek, this is Varani, a great musician.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe the greatest Bajor has ever known.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:28:24.411 --> 00:28:28.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She exaggerates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but that's why I'm so fond of her.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:28:30.708 --> 00:28:31.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Being a Bajoran</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:28:32.377 --> 00:28:35.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know what it's like to be displaced.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:28:36.798 --> 00:28:38.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As a token of friendship</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:28:39.676 --> 00:28:41.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would like to give you this.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:28:44.180 --> 00:28:47.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( playing quiet melody )</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:28:48.435 --> 00:28:53.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's from a concert I played</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>many years ago at the Jalanda Forum.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:29:09.247 --> 00:29:11.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Tumak, where have you been?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Nowhere.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:29:11.458 --> 00:29:13.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where are you going?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-To wash.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:29:24.596 --> 00:29:25.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer...</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:29:27.140 --> 00:29:29.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please show me a chart</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of this star system.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:29:39.194 --> 00:29:41.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-So, what'd your dad say?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-About what?</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:29:41.446 --> 00:29:42.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>About you getting in trouble with Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:29:43.031 --> 00:29:45.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He was very angry.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-He was?</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:29:45.158 --> 00:29:46.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He always gets angry</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when I get caught.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:29:49.662 --> 00:29:53.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping ) I just remembered.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have some errands to run for my uncle.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:29:54.042 --> 00:29:55.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're going to have to face them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sooner or later.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:29:56.628 --> 00:29:58.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was very funny, what you did.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:29:59.672 --> 00:30:02.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see, Jake?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>There's a man with a sense of humor.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:30:04.344 --> 00:30:05.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nobody's laughing.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:30:06.179 --> 00:30:07.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And luckily nobody got hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:30:08.181 --> 00:30:10.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think my friend's real sorry</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for what he did.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:30:12.977 --> 00:30:13.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aren't you?</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:30:15.063 --> 00:30:16.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:30:17.148 --> 00:30:18.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>See? What'd I tell you?</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:30:18.858 --> 00:30:21.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He doesn't sound sorry to me.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:30:25.323 --> 00:30:26.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( squealing )</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:30:36.000 --> 00:30:38.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:30:38.628 --> 00:30:43.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's enough. Break it up.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I said, break it up!</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:30:45.802 --> 00:30:47.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( snarling )</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:30:47.178 --> 00:30:48.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( growls )</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:30:48.930 --> 00:30:51.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's bad enough you're all hanging</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around the station</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:30:51.683 --> 00:30:54.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>without buying anything.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have to start fighting, too?</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:30:54.769 --> 00:30:56.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought we were welcome here.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:30:56.896 --> 00:30:59.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, make yourself</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>welcome somewhere else.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:31:00.775 --> 00:31:01.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't want us here.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:31:02.569 --> 00:31:04.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't want anything to do with us.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:31:04.863 --> 00:31:07.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, we don't want</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>anything to do with you.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:31:08.741 --> 00:31:09.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Any of you!</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:31:10.159 --> 00:31:10.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>yells </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:31:11.494 --> 00:31:12.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>hisses </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:31:15.290 --> 00:31:16.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>QUARK: I can see the Skrreeans</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:31:16.916 --> 00:31:19.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>don't bother to teach</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their children manners.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:31:19.252 --> 00:31:20.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>hisses </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:31:22.046 --> 00:31:24.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Dax and I have been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>combing through data on every uninhabited</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:31:24.674 --> 00:31:26.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>M-Class planet in the sector.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:31:26.342 --> 00:31:27.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We think that Draylon II</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:31:27.635 --> 00:31:29.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>would make a perfect home</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the Skrreea.</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:31:30.805 --> 00:31:33.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Draylon II? I've never heard of it.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:31:33.600 --> 00:31:36.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's near Sefalla Prime.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's got definite possibilities.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:31:36.978 --> 00:31:41.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stable orbit, temperate climate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and a very low surface radiation.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:31:41.691 --> 00:31:44.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Add to that good soil</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and a long growing season.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:31:44.944 --> 00:31:46.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it's our best bet.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:31:50.491 --> 00:31:52.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:31:58.207 --> 00:31:59.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-May we come in?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:32:09.802 --> 00:32:10.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ladies.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:32:13.598 --> 00:32:17.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive them, Commander Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They don't mean any disrespect.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:32:17.894 --> 00:32:18.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:32:19.270 --> 00:32:22.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have some encouraging news.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We think we've found a planet</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:32:22.774 --> 00:32:25.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for you and your people,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one with excellent potential</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:32:25.401 --> 00:32:26.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for resettlement.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:32:29.364 --> 00:32:34.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We appreciate all your hard work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm afraid it was unnecessary.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:32:35.036 --> 00:32:37.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see, we found Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:32:38.331 --> 00:32:39.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You did?</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:32:40.124 --> 00:32:42.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A planet of sorrow, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see?</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:32:43.753 --> 00:32:47.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kentanna is your planet.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kentanna is Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:32:57.600 --> 00:33:01.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Station Log, Stardate 47391.2.</i></c.bg_transparent>

492
00:33:01.729 --> 00:33:03.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Chief O'Brien is continuing</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to oversee repairs</i></c.bg_transparent>

493
00:33:03.815 --> 00:33:05.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>to the Skrreean ships docked</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>at the station.</i></c.bg_transparent>

494
00:33:06.067 --> 00:33:08.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Meanwhile, Minister Rozahn</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and Vedek Sorad have arrived</i></c.bg_transparent>

495
00:33:08.778 --> 00:33:12.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>from Bajor with an official response</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to the Skrreeans' request to immigrate.</i></c.bg_transparent>

496
00:33:13.199 --> 00:33:15.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Major, if I may have a moment?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm sorry, Varani.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:33:16.077 --> 00:33:17.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm on my way to a meeting.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:33:17.745 --> 00:33:20.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, with Minister Rozahn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and Vedek Sorad.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:33:20.581 --> 00:33:23.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I presume Haneek will be there as well.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:33:23.876 --> 00:33:27.088 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please tell here that my heart</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>goes out to her and her people.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:33:28.006 --> 00:33:31.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell her how much Bajorans everywhere</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>regret having to refuse their request.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:33:32.135 --> 00:33:35.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Aren't you being a little premature?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Am I? You know what</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:33:35.221 --> 00:33:37.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the provisional government's answer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is going to be.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:33:37.473 --> 00:33:40.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>These are people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who have lost everything, Varani.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:33:40.309 --> 00:33:43.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, and I wish there was some way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we could help them.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:33:45.189 --> 00:33:49.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Bajor is in shambles, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know that as well as I do.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:33:53.614 --> 00:33:55.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>First of all, I want you all to know</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:33:56.075 --> 00:33:58.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that the provisional government</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has taken the Skrreeans' request</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:33:58.995 --> 00:34:01.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for immigration very seriously.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:34:02.874 --> 00:34:06.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The debate in the Chamber of Ministers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>became quite heated at times.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:34:07.253 --> 00:34:10.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Though I suppose you could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>say that about all of our debates.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:34:10.173 --> 00:34:11.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But a decision was reached?</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:34:12.091 --> 00:34:15.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, I was sent here to tell you</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:34:15.553 --> 00:34:17.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that the Ministers, in accord</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the Vedek Assembly,</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:34:18.639 --> 00:34:21.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>have decided</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to deny the Skrreeans' request.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:34:22.310 --> 00:34:23.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ROZAHN: I am sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:34:24.020 --> 00:34:27.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor simply cannot absorb</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>three million refugees</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:34:27.899 --> 00:34:28.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>at this time.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:34:28.983 --> 00:34:31.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After what the Cardassians</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>did to our planet</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:34:31.736 --> 00:34:33.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we can barely take care of our own.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:34:33.863 --> 00:34:36.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But no one is asking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you to take care of us.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:34:36.866 --> 00:34:37.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This decision is not based</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:34:38.534 --> 00:34:41.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>strictly on Bajoran self-interest.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:34:42.455 --> 00:34:44.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Such a huge increase in population</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:34:44.540 --> 00:34:47.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>would prove to be tragic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your people as well as ours.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:34:47.502 --> 00:34:49.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Bajor has more than enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>room for us.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:34:49.754 --> 00:34:53.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The plains of the Northwest Peninsula</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are practically uninhabited.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:34:53.466 --> 00:34:54.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The land's ideal for farming.</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:34:55.384 --> 00:34:56.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It used to be</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:34:57.220 --> 00:34:59.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>before the Cardassians</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>got their hands on it.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:35:00.014 --> 00:35:03.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Minister Rozahn,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Skrreea are farmers.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:35:03.726 --> 00:35:05.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just give us the land.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:35:05.103 --> 00:35:07.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guarantee you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can make it thrive again.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:35:08.189 --> 00:35:11.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Under ideal circumstances,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>perhaps you could.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:35:11.776 --> 00:35:14.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But what if the circumstances</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aren't ideal?</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:35:15.238 --> 00:35:17.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if we go through</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another long winter?</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:35:17.490 --> 00:35:19.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if your crops fail?</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:35:19.575 --> 00:35:20.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if the famine</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:35:20.868 --> 00:35:23.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that has been plaguing Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>continues to spread?</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:35:23.788 --> 00:35:24.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What then?</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:35:25.540 --> 00:35:27.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are willing to take that risk.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:35:27.583 --> 00:35:28.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ROZAHN: I'm afraid we aren't.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:35:29.085 --> 00:35:30.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We ran a series of projections</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:35:30.878 --> 00:35:33.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to see whether a Skrreean</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>settlement could survive</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:35:33.089 --> 00:35:34.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on the Northwest peninsula.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:35:35.341 --> 00:35:37.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The results were not encouraging.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:35:38.678 --> 00:35:39.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Haneek?</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:35:39.804 --> 00:35:41.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you should seriously consider</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:35:41.556 --> 00:35:43.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Draylon II as an alternate to Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:35:43.683 --> 00:35:46.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The winters are mild.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>There's plenty of good farmland.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:35:46.644 --> 00:35:49.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No! Projections can be wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:35:49.981 --> 00:35:52.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SORAD: But what if they're not?</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:35:52.150 --> 00:35:55.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is Bajor to do if your people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>start dying?</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:35:56.112 --> 00:35:59.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought I made that clear.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We are not expecting your help.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:35:59.615 --> 00:36:02.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you really think we could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>stand by and do nothing?</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:36:03.035 --> 00:36:06.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We would feel obligated to help</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with food, with clothing</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:36:06.622 --> 00:36:10.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-with whatever it would take.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And where would that aid come from?</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:36:10.751 --> 00:36:12.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SORAD: Our resources are already depleted.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:36:13.296 --> 00:36:16.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To help you would mean</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>depriving our own people.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:36:17.216 --> 00:36:20.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am afraid the decision</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the provisional government is final.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:36:21.804 --> 00:36:24.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Skrreea will have to find somewhere</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>else to live.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:36:27.018 --> 00:36:30.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, talk to them.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:36:30.396 --> 00:36:31.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell them they're wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:36:34.025 --> 00:36:35.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Help us.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:36:38.946 --> 00:36:40.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:36:42.325 --> 00:36:43.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, Haneek...</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:36:45.036 --> 00:36:46.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But they're right. I wish they weren't.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:36:47.205 --> 00:36:49.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish Bajor was Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:36:51.334 --> 00:36:52.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But it's not.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:36:56.047 --> 00:36:58.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's still Draylon II.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:37:09.060 --> 00:37:10.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh!</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:37:10.519 --> 00:37:11.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look at this!</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:37:17.401 --> 00:37:18.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:37:20.655 --> 00:37:22.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you like cake</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the icoberry torte is really good.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:37:23.658 --> 00:37:25.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that big-eared troll</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>really your friend?</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:37:25.910 --> 00:37:27.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeah.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-He's an idiot.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:37:28.079 --> 00:37:29.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not the first to say that.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:37:30.122 --> 00:37:32.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But he's not such a bad guy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>once you get to know him.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:37:33.251 --> 00:37:35.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't plan on being</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around here that long.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:37:36.212 --> 00:37:38.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My dad says you're probably</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>going to Draylon II.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:37:38.589 --> 00:37:39.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Does he?</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:37:39.924 --> 00:37:41.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, sounds like a nice place.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:37:42.260 --> 00:37:43.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you want to move there?</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:37:43.761 --> 00:37:44.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:37:45.471 --> 00:37:46.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Neither do I.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:37:53.062 --> 00:37:54.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:37:55.147 --> 00:37:56.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:38:03.781 --> 00:38:05.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek...</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:38:07.493 --> 00:38:09.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The thing I don't understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is why you pretended</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:38:10.037 --> 00:38:11.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to be my friend.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:38:11.998 --> 00:38:12.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wasn't pretending.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:38:14.458 --> 00:38:15.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah!</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:38:15.501 --> 00:38:17.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you are my friend...</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:38:18.170 --> 00:38:19.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Until I need you.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:38:24.427 --> 00:38:28.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know it's hard for you to see right now</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I am trying to help.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:38:28.431 --> 00:38:30.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think I've had quite enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your help.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:38:31.517 --> 00:38:32.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've got to believe me.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:38:32.893 --> 00:38:35.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Sisko has found</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you a wonderful home.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:38:36.063 --> 00:38:37.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You betrayed me, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:38:38.316 --> 00:38:39.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I didn't.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:38:40.484 --> 00:38:42.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I honestly believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the provisional government</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:38:42.653 --> 00:38:43.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>made the right decision</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:38:43.988 --> 00:38:45.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>both for Bajor and the Skrreeans.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:38:46.532 --> 00:38:49.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If that's true,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we have nothing more to discuss.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:38:53.372 --> 00:38:55.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was hoping we could still be friends.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:38:56.584 --> 00:38:59.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So in other words, you came here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>looking for forgiveness.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:39:01.589 --> 00:39:03.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I don't forgive you.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:39:06.427 --> 00:39:07.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sisko to Kira.</i></c.bg_transparent>

609
00:39:08.346 --> 00:39:09.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:39:09.722 --> 00:39:10.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Is Haneek with you?</i></c.bg_transparent>

611
00:39:11.098 --> 00:39:11.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:39:12.016 --> 00:39:15.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I need both of you in Ops immediately.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tumak has taken a ship.</i></c.bg_transparent>

613
00:39:15.686 --> 00:39:16.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>He's headed for Bajor.</i></c.bg_transparent>

614
00:39:35.164 --> 00:39:37.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-They're not responding, sir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Keep trying, Mr. O'Brien.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:39:37.541 --> 00:39:38.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did this happen?</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:39:38.918 --> 00:39:40.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>With all the traffic around the station</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:39:40.795 --> 00:39:42.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak and two of his friends</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were able to slip away.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:39:42.963 --> 00:39:46.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We didn't even know the ship was gone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until the Bajorans contacted us.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:39:46.509 --> 00:39:49.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek, I need for you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to try to talk to your son.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:39:49.428 --> 00:39:51.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a high-energy radiation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>leak in the port nacelle.</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:39:52.348 --> 00:39:54.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've tried to make him aware of it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but he refuses to acknowledge us.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:39:55.184 --> 00:39:57.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, open a channel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Skrreean vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:39:58.020 --> 00:39:59.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:40:01.399 --> 00:40:02.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ready.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:40:05.653 --> 00:40:06.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak?</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:40:08.572 --> 00:40:09.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Listen to me.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:40:11.700 --> 00:40:13.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your ship's in danger.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:40:14.203 --> 00:40:17.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( quietly ) Have him turn off</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>his engines and drift</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:40:17.206 --> 00:40:18.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>until the Bajorans can tractor him in.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:40:20.042 --> 00:40:23.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, turn off your engines.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:40:23.754 --> 00:40:27.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must turn your engines off, now!</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:40:28.592 --> 00:40:29.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not responding.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:40:30.469 --> 00:40:32.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, this is serious!</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:40:33.097 --> 00:40:34.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your life is in danger.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:40:34.723 --> 00:40:37.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The others who are with you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their lives are in danger.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:40:37.143 --> 00:40:39.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please! Answer me!</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:40:39.728 --> 00:40:41.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( console beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:40:41.730 --> 00:40:44.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sensors are detecting two Bajoran vessels</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>closing in on the Skrreean ship.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:40:44.859 --> 00:40:49.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Display it here. Mr. O'Brien,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>patch us into the Bajoran interceptor.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:40:49.363 --> 00:40:50.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'BRIEN: Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:40:50.489 --> 00:40:52.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>BAJORAN: Entered restricted space.</i></c.bg_transparent>

642
00:40:52.408 --> 00:40:54.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You must turn around</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and leave immediately.</i></c.bg_transparent>

643
00:40:54.493 --> 00:40:55.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open a channel.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:40:55.703 --> 00:40:58.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Major Kira</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Nerys on Deep Space 9.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:40:58.497 --> 00:41:00.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Skrreean vessel has refused</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to acknowledge our hails.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:41:01.083 --> 00:41:03.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Communications may be down.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have to let them land.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:41:03.878 --> 00:41:06.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>That's impossible, Major.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>We have strict orders</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>not to allow</i></c.bg_transparent>

648
00:41:06.255 --> 00:41:07.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>any Skrreean vessel to land.</i></c.bg_transparent>

649
00:41:08.048 --> 00:41:09.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The pilot's just a boy.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:41:09.175 --> 00:41:11.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He took the ship without permission.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's barely operational.</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:41:12.261 --> 00:41:14.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: We're not even sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he'll make it back here.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:41:14.096 --> 00:41:16.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm sorry, Major, but we have our orders.</i></c.bg_transparent>

653
00:41:16.223 --> 00:41:17.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who gave you those orders?</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:41:17.349 --> 00:41:18.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>They come directly from General Hazar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

655
00:41:18.976 --> 00:41:21.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax, get me General Hazar on Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:41:21.395 --> 00:41:24.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell his people it's an emergency.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I want to speak to him now.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:41:24.732 --> 00:41:25.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand by, interceptor.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:41:25.691 --> 00:41:28.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>General Hazar will be countermanding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>those orders any minute.</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:41:28.903 --> 00:41:31.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The interceptor is closing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the Skrreean ship.</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:41:34.366 --> 00:41:36.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's General Hazar, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:41:36.410 --> 00:41:37.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: On screen.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:41:37.495 --> 00:41:39.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>What is this about, Commander?</i></c.bg_transparent>

663
00:41:39.914 --> 00:41:42.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's about the Skrreean vessel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's approaching Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:41:42.458 --> 00:41:44.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I've already given the orders</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to have it turned back.</i></c.bg_transparent>

665
00:41:45.044 --> 00:41:48.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That ship is being flown by a child</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and it's leaking radiation.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:41:49.048 --> 00:41:49.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>A child?</i></c.bg_transparent>

667
00:41:49.965 --> 00:41:51.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PILOT: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Skrreean ship. Repeating.</i></c.bg_transparent>

668
00:41:51.675 --> 00:41:55.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Return to the space station now.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Have him shut down his engines.</i></c.bg_transparent>

669
00:41:55.387 --> 00:41:56.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We'll tow him back.</i></c.bg_transparent>

670
00:41:57.014 --> 00:42:00.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, please, turn your engines off.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:42:01.101 --> 00:42:02.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( shots firing )</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:42:02.478 --> 00:42:03.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interceptor One, what's going on?</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:42:04.188 --> 00:42:06.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>They've opened fire on us.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Taking evasive action.</i></c.bg_transparent>

674
00:42:06.565 --> 00:42:08.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tumak, don't do this!</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:42:08.108 --> 00:42:09.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>PILOT: We've been hit!</i></c.bg_transparent>

676
00:42:09.693 --> 00:42:11.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, they're returning fire.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:42:11.320 --> 00:42:12.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No!</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:42:12.363 --> 00:42:15.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Disengage, interceptor! Repeat, disengage.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:42:15.115 --> 00:42:18.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>General, tell your pilots</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to hold their fire.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:42:19.495 --> 00:42:20.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Relaying that order now.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:42:26.168 --> 00:42:27.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sobs )</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:42:29.547 --> 00:42:30.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interceptor One.</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:42:31.799 --> 00:42:34.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The Skrreean ship exploded.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>I didn't even think we hit it.</i></c.bg_transparent>

684
00:42:36.345 --> 00:42:38.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The phaser beam must've ignited</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the radiation leak.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:42:41.517 --> 00:42:43.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm very sorry, Commander.</i></c.bg_transparent>

686
00:42:44.478 --> 00:42:46.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We all are, General.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:43:20.014 --> 00:43:22.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just stopped by to wish</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you luck on Draylon II.</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:43:23.517 --> 00:43:27.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haneek, I still believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this is the best choice...</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:43:27.563 --> 00:43:29.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For Bajor and for you.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:43:30.316 --> 00:43:33.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You still believe we would have been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a burden to your people?</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:43:35.195 --> 00:43:36.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:43:36.947 --> 00:43:39.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you've made a terrible mistake.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:43:39.825 --> 00:43:40.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of you.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:43:41.285 --> 00:43:42.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we could have helped you.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:43:43.579 --> 00:43:45.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we could have helped each other.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:43:46.123 --> 00:43:50.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Skrreeans are farmers, Kira.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have a famine on your planet.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:43:51.211 --> 00:43:53.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps we could have made</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that peninsula bloom again.</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:43:55.007 --> 00:43:56.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HANEEK: We'll never know, will we?</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:43:57.509 --> 00:43:59.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fifty years of Cardassian rule</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:43:59.595 --> 00:44:02.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>have made you all frightened</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and suspicious.</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:44:04.558 --> 00:44:06.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel sorry for you.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:44:11.607 --> 00:44:12.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were right.</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:44:14.151 --> 00:44:15.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor is not Kentanna.</c.bg_transparent>

